      <li parentName="ul">{`The solution is a configuration that allows those forces to resolve themeselves.`}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>{`The pattern is both a process and a thing â€“ a thing which is alive, and a description of the process which creates that thing.`}</p>
    <p>{`To identify a pattern, we have to make the inner structure of the pattern clear. When we see a system or pattern 'working' out in the world, we should ask:`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`What is happening?`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Why is it helping to make the place feel alive?`}</li>
